-1 CRIMSON SOLDIERS~

In the times of the creation of Redemption, immortals roamed the worlds. In 
those days, wars were fought and gods perished. The orc immortal Amaranth 
had defeated many in his campaigns of war. In one such battle, Amaranth was 
cut and two drops of blood fell to the earth. From these two drops, two 
being formed. They were twins and were named Kingston and Helgriz. Seeing 
their father, they too wanted to wage war and were fiercely jealous of the 
powers of the immortals who have ruled Redemption. Kingston and Helgriz went 
underground and built an army for that Day, which they would emerge and 
faithfully shed the blood of the inhabitants of Redemption.
Our Day is now, and we shall see the rise of a new power and darkness in 
the realms of Redemption.
